  <section>
    <img src="/assets/personwithlaptop.svg" class="small-image" style="float: right;" alt="" />
    <p>I infrequently send out a newsletter with medium-length posts written by me, updates on courses, new blog and YouTube videos, my <em>best</em> coupons, and interesting and fun links.</p>
    <p>I won't share your email with anyone else. If you reply to a newsletter, I'll do my best to write back!</p>
    <p>You can unsubscribe at any time.</p>
  </section>
